data.description: Enter this single story gorgeous 2022 new construction home in prime West Lancaster location.  This 1,757 sq ft beauty has much to offer. As you step into the home on the luxury waterproof vinyl flooring you have clear sidelines, of the open concept living space. The kitchen at the heart of the home is fully upgraded with a custom backsplash, endless cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and an oversized island with quartz countertops. The island is a perfect place to sit and enjoy dinner or there is plenty of space for an oversize dining table between the living room and kitchen. The high ceiling living room has a dual pane sliding door that leads you to the private backyard with freshly done concrete, perfect for entertaining. Immediately to the right of the main entrance you see the office or potential 4th bedroom as well as the separate individual laundry room. To the left you have 2 spacious bedrooms and 1 bath as well as the door that leads to the 2-car attached garage.  Toward the back of the home, you find the master suite with an oversized walk-in closet with custom cabinets and a gorgeous bathroom with his/hers sinks.  Overall, this 7,345-lot home includes over $78K of upgrades that make the home a perfect find. See this beauty before it’s gone!
